{\b\fs30 STEP_2-occams_tree}\par
\par
\par
\par
{\b\fs26 Design (documented; not yet coded)}\par
\par
\li360  \u8226?  [x] Scope confirmed: orthogroups only, for now\par
\li360  \u8226?  [x] Per-tool standalone execution (Option A \u8212? one run per tool, compare downstream)\par
